Enum PrintType

  • Object
    • Enum<PrintType>
      • com.zebra.sdk.common.card.enumerations.PrintType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Comparable<PrintType>

    public enum PrintType
extends Enum<PrintType>
    Specifies the type of print to be performed for the given image data.
